  <brief_title>Single Intravenous Administration of TB-402 for the Prophylaxis of Venous Thromboembolic Events (VTE) After Total Knee Replacement Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single Intravenous Administration of TB-402 for the Prophylaxis of Venous Thromboembolic Events (VTE) After Total Knee Replacement Surgery: A Dose-Escalating, Multicenter, Randomised, Active- Controlled Open Label Study</official_title>
